and unwavering resolve. To hold $TIME is to embrace the philosophy that true wealth is not seized in a rush 
but nurtured over ages with steadfast patience.

The Essence of $TIME

Unlike other tokens that reward the quick and the reckless, 
$TIME bestows its blessings only upon those who understand that real value comes to those who wait. 
Governed by an ever-increasing max holding limit, 
the $TIME contract operates on a principle as ancient as the stars themselves: 
growth compounded through the passage of time.

